subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Lorena Ochoa shot a four-under 69 in windy conditions to take a one-stroke lead over Suzann Pettersen into the final round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s Corona Championship in Morelia, Mexico. Ochoa had a 20-under 199 total. After opening with consecutive bogey-free 65s, she had eight birdies, two bogeys and a double bogey.
